Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time spent on Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Average resolution time for cases involving Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR occurs

Name: Time difference between Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION for similar cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE for re-submission
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time from Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION to final Payment Handled
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum time taken for a case to be closed after Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Maximum time taken for a case to be closed after Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000002527E14D8B0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and any subsequent Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Total time for all activities to be completed after Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR occurs

Name: Average time for Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION in cases that require director approval
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR occurs

Name: Time from Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average handling time for Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION before re-submission or escalation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE occurs

Name: Time from Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION to Request Payment in cases where re-submission is successful
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Request Payment'
